1. *Celog* života sam se bavio sportom. (I have been doing sports my whole life.)
2. Ona je *celog* dana bila tužna. (She was sad the whole day.)
3. *Celog* dana nisam uspeo da završim posao. (I failed to finish the job the whole day.)
4. *Celog* vremena je bio tu. (He was there the whole time.)
5. *Celog* svojih snaga se trudio da uspe. (He tried with all his strength to succeed.)